
This directory contains host-side and firmware-adjacent tests for the keyswitch
tester firmware.

Current test suites:

- `test_protocol/` for command parsing
- `test_domain/` for homing and motion state logic
- `test_integration/` for command-to-domain interaction tests

Run all host tests with:

```powershell
Set-Location "c:\git\BTT SKR2 Testing"
& ".\test\run_host_tests.ps1"
```

These tests intentionally target the extracted `lib/keyswitch_core/` layer so
the critical behavior can be validated without requiring the SKR2 hardware.

Run live-board serial integration tests with:

```powershell
Set-Location "c:\git\BTT SKR2 Testing"
& ".\test\run_live_serial_tests.ps1"
```

Add `-IncludeMotion` when it is safe to execute `home` and `backoff` against the attached hardware.
